  <div class="feature-text">
    
      <p class="feature-title">Phylogeny and Evolution</p>
    
    
<p>There are &gt; 3,000 species of termites in this world, showing a great diversity of collective behavior. Comparison among them allows us to infer the history of evolution. We also love cool fossils.</p>

